public abstract class AbstractAgendaItemPopupMenu
extends javax.swing.JPopupMenu
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener

Provides the shell of a popup menu for agenda items in an agenda viewer. The viewer defines a subclass that fills in the abstract methods.
